This sets the max thrust to weight ratio we want to experience in flight.
This function takes into account the planet's current gravity, the crafts max thrust to mass ratio, and calculates the value that will keep the craft's TWR at ThrottleLimit.
It also takes into account the minimum value we want this to set the throttle to using MinThrottle. If the value provided by the equation is greater than it, it will use the MinThrottle value.
